// ========== README.md ==========
# REI Deal Machine - Wholesale & Subject-To System

A professional Progressive Web App (PWA) for managing real estate wholesale and subject-to deals, designed to help you achieve 3-5 deals per month and $35,000+ in monthly revenue.

## ðŸš€ Features

### Core Functionality
- **Lead Pipeline Management**: Track and manage all your leads with detailed information
- **Deal Analyzer**: Calculate MAO (Maximum Allowable Offer) and analyze deal profitability
- **Marketing Campaign Tracking**: Monitor PPC, cold calling, SMS, and direct mail campaigns
- **Contract Management**: Store and track purchase agreements and assignment contracts
- **Buyers List**: Maintain a database of cash buyers and investors
- **Dashboard Analytics**: Real-time stats on leads, profits, and performance
- **PWA Capabilities**: Works offline, installable on mobile/desktop

### Business Logic
- **MAO Calculation**: Automatically calculates using the 70% rule
- **Profit Estimation**: Instant profit calculations for wholesale and subject-to deals
- **Lead Scoring**: Motivation-based lead prioritization (Hot/Warm/Cold)
- **Marketing ROI**: Track cost per lead and conversion rates

